'''Gamorrean opera''' was a form of [[Opera/Legends|opera]] performed by [[Gamorrean/Legends|Gamorreans]] that was composed of deep grunts, snorts and growls.<ref name="Hutt">{{FFG|story=The Long Arm of the Hutt|book=Star Wars: Edge of the Empire Beginner Game|text=''Star Wars: Edge of the Empire'' Beginner Game}}</ref>

Although the genre was generally regarded as obnoxious<ref name="Isard">''[[X-Wing: Isard's Revenge]]''</ref> and failed to find a significant appreciative audience across [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]],<ref name="blog">{{SW|url=news/slugthrowers-an-overview-of-popular-music-and-musicians-in-a-galaxy-far-far-away-part-1|series=Slugthrowers: An Overview of Popular Music and Musicians in a Galaxy Far, Far Away|text=Part 1|nolive=1}}</ref> [[Trandoshan/Legends|Trandoshan]] [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] [[Trex]] liked listening to Gamorrean opera during long [[Realspace/Legends|space]] journeys.<ref name="Hutt" />

